Class QuestionnaireResponseJob

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.birbit.android.jobqueue.Job

        • ch.usz.c3pro.c3_pro_android_framework.questionnaire.jobs.QuestionnaireResponseJob
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class QuestionnaireResponseJob
extends LoadResultJob<org.hl7.fhir.dstu3.model.QuestionnaireResponse>
    This job is used by the DataQueue to convert ResearchStack TaskResult to a FHIR QuestionnaireResponse in a background thread. The handler will move the result to the main (UI) thread, so it can be used to update the UI.
